Medicare API Endpoint Classes

Source: R/S7_care.R
medicare.Rd

Medicare API Endpoint Classes

Usage

care_endpoint(alias)

care_temporal(alias)

pro_endpoint(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> endpoint alias

Value

An S7 <care_endpoint>, or <care_temporal> object

Examples

care_endpoint("care_dialysis")
